{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And mostly my little brother is the one that kept lifting me up and getting me to get some air.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was lucky enough to find a spot not too far away, and he-- he took care of me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He took care of me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and this is how we got to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we got-- we left the 1st of August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The reason I know that, I looked up-- I looked up some records, and my brothers, well, naturally, they-- they told me about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They weren't 100% sure exactly on the dates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We weren't exactly counting calendars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- but I know it was August 1 that we-- we went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we got-- when we-- we got there, naturally, they separated the men from the women right away first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they took us into a building in Auschwitz, and I have my own child's memory of that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- it was an eye-opener for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I have never seen anything like it, even though I've seen so much already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was exposed to death and killings and-- and everything else before and being myself exposed to death.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I've never seen anything like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was completely novel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When I watched-- when I watched those Germans walking amongst us, the women, I must have been a great observer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because I remember they went around immaculately dressed with their boots, which is one of my nemesis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And boots really destroy me when I hear that sound.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I can almost identify it very clearly in today's-- even today.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I hear this kind of sound.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It gives me the chills.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they walked around immaculately dressed with their pokes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
